- JwtUtil: generate + validate HS256 tokens (jjwt 0.12.6)
- JwtAuthFilter: stateless Bearer token extraction per request
- UserDetailsServiceImpl: loads user by email, maps Role → ROLE_ prefix
- SecurityConfig: stateless JWT filter chain, RBAC, CORS for localhost:5173
