- RefreshTokenService: secure random token, SHA-256 hashed, single-session
- AuthController: POST /api/auth/register, /login, /refresh
- GlobalExceptionHandler: @RestControllerAdvice, consistent ApiErrorResponse
- Exception hierarchy: ApiException, Duplicate/InvalidCredentials/NotFound/Token
- DTOs: RegisterRequest, LoginRequest, RefreshTokenRequest, AuthResponse
- application-dev.properties: JWT secret + expiry config (15min / 7day)
